---

<section
  class="relative py-4 sm:py-8 md:py-12 min-h-dvh max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"
>
  <!-- Main content container with responsive layout -->
  <div
    class="relative grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 justify-between gap-4 xl:gap-0"
  >
    <!-- Text content column -->
    <div
      class="col-span-2 order-1 flex flex-col justify-center space-y-2 sm:space-y-4 w-full"
    >
      <h1
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-primary leading-tight text-balance motion-preset-blur-right motion-duration-1500 motion-delay-2000"
        style="font-size: clamp(1.875rem, 4vw + 1rem, 2.4rem);"
      >
        Creamos la página web profesional que tu empresa necesita
      </h1>

      <p
        class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-secondary font-medium text-balance leading-relaxed motion-preset-blur-right motion-duration-1600 motion-delay-2500"
        style="font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw + 0.5rem, 1.2rem);"
      >
        Tu web es la puerta de entrada a tu negocio. Haz que te encuentren y
        confíen desde el primer clic.
      </p>

      <div class="pt-2">
        <Button
          className="font-semibold motion-scale-in-0 motion-opacity-in-0 motion-delay-2700 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200"
        >
          Quiero mi página web
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card demonstration column -->
    <div
      class="order-2 relative max-w-xs w-full h-[250px] sm:h-[300px] md:h-[400px] lg:h-[500px] motion-opacity-in-0 motion-delay-3000"
    >
      <CardSwapDemo
        cardDistance={15}
        verticalDistance={25}
        skewAmount={4}
        width={800}
        height={600}
        delay={8000}
        pauseOnHover={false}
        items={cardItems}
        client:only="react"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
